pg_tre (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release candidate.
  * Native PostgreSQL 18+ index access method for approximate regex.
  * Three-tier filter funnel: range bloom, sparsemap trigram postings,
    per-tuple bloom.
  * Ships legacy tre_amatch() UDFs for compatibility.

